http://www.vogella.com/tutorials/Gradle/article.html

gradle wrapper  搞一个wrapper

# 1.入门

gradle init  生成一个项目
gradle init -dsl

## create a task
创建一个将src文件夹拷贝到dest的任务

```
task copy(type: Copy, group: "Custom", description: "copy source to dest") {
  from "src"
  into "dest"
}
```

运行 ./gradlew copy

## apply a plugin

```
plugins {
  id "base"
}

task zip(type: Zip, group: "Archive", description: "Archives sources in a zip file") {
    from "src"
    setArchiveName "basic-demo-1.0.zip"
}
```

运行 ./gradlew zip

## discover your tasks
./gradlew tasks

## 可用的properties
./gradlew properties

修改两个属性看看

```
description "A trivial Gradle build"
version 1.0
```

# 2.构建一个Java项目

## 构建java application

gradle init --type java-application

build项目 ./gradlew build

运行项目 ./gradlew run




## 构建java library

gradle init --type java-library --project-name jvm-library

build项目 ./gradlew build

检查一下打好的jar包 jar tf build/libs/jvm-library.jar
检查一下manifest文件 jar xf build/libs/jvm-library-0.1.0.jar META-INF/MANIFEST.MF

修改一下build.gradle看看，加上一行  version = '0.1.0' 再运行 ./gradlew jar

#### 配置jar任务
```
jar {
    manifest {
        attributes('Implementation-Title': project.name,
                   'Implementation-Version': project.version)
    }
}
```

## spring boot项目

```
gradle init  --type java-application
```



